snippet.title: Pantheon: Rise of the Fallen Pre-Alpha 2 Gameplay w/ CohhCarnage
snippet.description:
This stream was taken during a live pre-alpha 2 session in Halnir Cave. The group attempts (and wipes to) several boss encounters and  ultimately determines that Pantheon is TOUGH. 

For more information and to pledge to make this project a reality, visit us at https://pantheonmmo.com
